title: Tree Covered Hillside Overlooking Port and Harbor Town
provenance: Anna Richards Brewster, Scarsdale, NY, 1905-1952; William T. Brewster,
description: View from a hilltop. Prominent tree in right foreground, second group of trees in left distance atop a second hill.  Below, a river flowing from left, back behind second hill; across the river, outlines of town on left.
name: Sketchbook folio
